						<div class="postbody">Movax12 found the bug. Your LDA EMPHASIS line is loading the RAM value at $20, not the literal value. Change it to LDA #EMPHASIS and it might start working again.<br /><br />I agree that proper initialization is important. Even the most basic of experiment programs needs to have complete initialization or you'll start to have strange errors, especially if you test on the more accurate emulators.</div>

